<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.7.1">
<l>paṇṭaināṉ maṟaiyum vēḷviyuṅ kēḷvip pataṅkaḷum pataṅkaḷiṉ poruḷum</l>
<l>piṇṭamāy virinta piṟaṅkoḷi yaṉalum perukiya puṉaloṭu nilaṉum</l>
<l>koṇṭalmā rutamuṅ kuraikaṭa lēḻu mēḻumā malaikaḷum vicumpum</l>
<l>aṇṭamum tāṉāy niṉṟavem perumā ṉaraṅkamā nakaramarn tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who lies calmly in the great city of Araṅkam is our lord who endures</l>
<l>As the ancient four Vedas, the sacrifice, words of [sacred] learning,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the meaning of [those] words,</l>
<l>A bright growing fire which expands as a sphere, the earth with rising waters,</l>
<l>Clouds, wind, the seven roaring seas, seven huge mountains, the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the universe.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
